                "game-id": "6a30ff50ed821ab5b9699b2f3d68c0d6",
                "text": "This magic comes from the arcane tradition, which is built on logic and rationality. Anything with this trait is magical.  \n  \nA creature with this trait is primarily constituted of or has a strong connection to arcane magic.",
